{"tid":1474321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國難五金第三店重啟公告","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:05:43.000Z","uid":296349,"like":115,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"59ca9fd53df4fa1963e0a6a9f08009b3fde35dcc","tid":1474321,"uid":296349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"國難五金第三店重啟公告<br />\n<br />\n由於國難五金腦細李政𤋮，死性不改，資金過盛，上次大埔店的虧蝕太少，決定屢敗屢戰，為表愛國情操、振興經濟、推動自由之遊行，擬定於「紅土」區再次開舖，捲土重來。另有更多新品上市，務求滿足瞬息萬變的市場走勢。<br />\n<br />\n鑒於本舖仍在始創階段，將會繼續採取惡徳商人營商策略，貴買平賣，以本傷人打擊同業；同時貴買貴賣坑殺恩客，大賺特賺，實際運作全屬腦細心情決定。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各界再次蒞臨惠顧。<br />\n<br />\n另特此邀請全家死絕的香港警察再次到舖為國難五金貨品驗證及宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n「紅土店」的詳細地址請密切留意 國難五金Facebook 專頁及IG有關公佈。<br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/國難五金-100634091287214/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%A3%E4%BA%94%E9%87%91-100634091287214%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=f6377106\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/國難五金-100634091287214/</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/gwok3naan6ng5gam1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgwok3naan6ng5gam1&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=c14237f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gwok3naan6ng5gam1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金關公部負責人暨武術指導<br />\n黎占<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOMgQfG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOMgQfG.jpg&h=d1193625&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa06dd66d2a179f3cb47b7c333c15440ff65e339","tid":1474321,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56a51494605c04f8e3a74143aaf0d16668d5a94","tid":1474321,"uid":6801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以瘋狂買野"},{"pid":"9d65